data.text: @RaeDeAnneR What KDrama are you on now? I'm trying to decide what to watch next?
@CharlesGriswo13 Thank you. I’m trying! Thankfully I have help. ☺️
@RaeDeAnneR Long COVID is nasty. Take care of yourself.
(The bigger parts though are my partner, who has had to pick up a lot of my slack when I just *can’t*, and my cats, who comfort me constantly with their presence, cuteness, and love.)
